::DarkMouse/KitKat/SHadowWing::

DarkMouse::
She stood there waiting for BlackAracnia to show her the way to 
Quickstrike.
-------------------

KitKat::
She Looked around. "Well, let's get this thing back on me.  I need to 
be a four legged wolf, not a three legged one."
-------------------

Shadow Wing::
She walked back and checked on Lunarpine in the CR chamber.  She 
smiled. He was not just a little scratched up when she went to him in 
the woods.  She knew there was somthing that he wasn't telling her. 
He got into a scrap with a pred or something, she thought.  She would 
get it all from him when he was out of the CR.
